productReviews.reviewText: I tried to attack it but got meatball all over it.
I tried to pinch it but got peanut all over it.
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
one of my hobbies is baking. and when i'm baking this works great.
